  <h3>ITIL ST Service Validation and Testing</h3>
  <p><i><a href="/home/itilst">Back to ITIL Service Transition</a></i></p>
  <hr>
  <p><b><span id="Overview">Objective:</span></b> The objective of <span id="md-webpage-description" itemprop="description"><i>Service Validation and Testing</i> is to ensure that deployed Releases and the resulting services meet customer expectations. This ITIL process verifies that IT operations is able to support the new service.</span></p>
